        "action": "To create buffer zones around schools, stopping intimidation of staff & children",
        "additional_details": "We think there have been a number of protests that have caused intimidation of school staff.",
        "background": "On the 25th March 2024, the Khan Review recommended the creation of a 150m buffer zone around schools to prevent protests happening directly outside of school gates. We think the recommendations should be implemented asap, with allowances for protests at the weekend and outside school hours.",
